		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />yes there are 3 ppu cycles in one cpu cycle (for ntsc, not pal)
<br />
<br />a cpu instruction has more than one cpu cycle.  i think you got it right.
<br />
<br />so you dont burn your bridges, i wouldnt hard code 1 cpu cycle to 3 ppu cycles.  you wont be able to add pal supppor later on.
<br />
<br />what do you have started now ?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
